@page "/AboutUs"

<div class="about-section">
    <!-- Background Section with Title -->
    <div class="background">
        <h1>About Us</h1>
    </div>

    <!-- Content Section -->
    <div class="content-container">
        <div class="content-row">
            <!-- Profile Image -->
            <div class="profile-image">
                <img src="Images/professionalGuard.png" alt="Agent">
                <!-- Experience Highlight Section -->
                <div class="experience-highlight">
                    <h3 style="font-size:96px;">20+</h3>
                    <p style="color:white;">years of experience</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Text Content -->
            <div class="text-content">
                <h2>Who we are</h2>
                <p style="text-align: justify; line-height:2.5rem; font-size:16px;">
                    GIO-14 Group of Intelligence and Operations-14 is a British company with headquarters in the UK. Our agents are highly trained ex-special forces and ex-members from the police. 
                    </p>
                <p style="text-align: justify; line-height:2.5rem; font-size:16px;">
                    We have the latest technology to help us track, locate, and if necessary, retrieve fugitives or persons of interest.
                    GIO-14 has a close relationship with government authorities in South America. 
                 </p>

                <p style="text-align: justify; line-height:2.5rem; font-size:16px;">
                    With mutual cooperation, GIO-14 is able to locate, and if necessary, retrieve a fugitive or a person of interest.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        
    </div>

    <div class="info-section">
        <div class="info-box">
            <h3>Our Mission</h3>
            <p>
                To provide highly effective and reliable intelligence and operational solutions that prioritize safety, accuracy, and efficiency. We aim to foster security by working closely with authorized agencies and adhering strictly to both local and international legal frameworks. Every operation we undertake is guided by a commitment to excellence and respect for confidentiality.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="info-box">
            <h3>Our Expertise</h3>
            <p>
                At GIO-14, we pride ourselves on our elite team of agents, all of whom are former members of special forces and law enforcement agencies. Their rigorous training, extensive field experience, and specialized skill sets make them highly capable in high-stakes situations, from intelligence gathering to tactical retrieval. Our agents are accustomed to operating in challenging environments and handling complex cases, which has made us a trusted partner for high-profile clients worldwide.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="core-values-section">
        <!-- Core Values Header -->
        <div class="core-values-header">
            <h2>Our Core Values</h2>
        </div>

        <!-- Core Values Icons and Descriptions -->
        <div class="core-values-icons">
            <div class="core-value-item">
                <img src="/Images/puzzle_5191945.svg" alt="integrity" />
                <p>Integrity</p>
            </div>
            <div class="core-value-item">
                <img src="/Images/shield_4594138.svg" alt="shield" />
                <p>Professionalism</p>
            </div>
            <div class="core-value-item">
                <img src="/Images/padlock_11273108.svg" alt="confidentiality"/>
                <p>Confidentiality</p>
            </div>
            <div class="core-value-item">
                <img src="/Images/goal_14126776.svg" alt="Commitment to Excellence" />
                <p>Commitment to Excellence</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="why-choose-us-section">
        <!-- Section Title -->
        <h2>Why Choose Us</h2>

        <!-- Content Row -->
        <div class="content-row_">
            <!-- Text Content -->
            <div class="text-content_">
                <h3>Proven Expertise</h3>
                <p>
                    We understand that our clients need results they can rely on. Our agents are former special forces and law enforcement professionals who bring decades of field experience and specialized skills to each mission. Their expertise allows us to handle even the most complex cases with a high level of precision and confidence, ensuring that our clients receive effective and reliable solutions.
                </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Icons -->
            <div class="icon-content">
                <img src="/Images/talent-management_17277999.png" />
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>


</div>




